- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is also likely as motif counting is an important task in network analysis and the paper discusses the scalability of the algorithm to very large graphs.
- cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) is another possible category as the paper mentions the use of color coding in computational biology and chemistry.

- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is a possible category as the paper deals with graph theory and combinatorics, which are topics in discrete mathematics.
